B.WU=new A.cz("1. Data Collection\nTixon collects personal information that you voluntarily provide when you register for an account, purchase a ticket, or interact with the platform. This may include your name, email address, phone number, and payment information. We may also collect non-personally identifiable information such as your IP address and device type for analytical purposes.\n\n",null,B.ag,null,null,null,null,null,null)
B.WS=new A.cz("2. Usage of Data\nYour personal information is used to:\n- Facilitate ticket purchases and event registrations.\n- Communicate with you regarding your bookings or events.\n- Provide customer support.\n- Improve our platform and services through analytics.\nWe may also send you promotional material or updates regarding new events and features unless you opt out of such communications.\n\n",null,B.ag,null,null,null,null,null,null)
B.WY=new A.cz("3. Cookies & Tracking\nTixon uses cookies to enhance your browsing experience and to personalize content. Cookies help us remember your preferences and log-in details. You can choose to disable cookies in your browser settings, but this may affect the functionality of the platform.\n\n",null,B.ag,null,null,null,null,null,null)
B.WA=new A.cz("4. Third-Party Sharing\nWe may share your data with third-party service providers such as payment processors, event organizers, and cloud hosting services. These parties are required to protect your data and use it only for the purposes outlined in this policy.\n\n",null,B.ag,null,null,null,null,null,null)
B.Wz=new A.cz("5. Data Security\nWe take data security seriously and implement industry-standard measures to protect your information from unauthorized access, disclosure, or misuse. However, no online platform can guarantee 100% security, and you use Tixon at your own risk.\n\n",null,B.ag,null,null,null,null,null,null)
B.WI=new A.cz("6. User Rights\nYou have the right to access, update, or delete your personal information at any time by logging into your account. If you wish to deactivate your account or have questions regarding your data, please contact us.\n\n",null,B.ag,null,null,null,null,null,null)
B.WG=new A.cz("7. Age Restrictions\nTixon is intended for use by college students. Users under the age of 18 must have permission from a parent or guardian to use the platform.",null,B.ag,null,null,null,null,null,null)
B.J0=A.a(s([B.WU,B.WS,B.WY,B.WA,B.Wz,B.WI,B.WG]),t.p)
