B.WB=new A.cz("1. Acceptance of Terms\nBy accessing or using the Tixon website or mobile application, you agree to comply with these Terms & Conditions. If you do not agree, please do not use our services. Tixon reserves the right to modify these terms at any time, and such modifications will take effect upon posting. It is your responsibility to review these terms regularly.\n\n",null,B.ag,null,null,null,null,null,null)
B.Wy=new A.cz("2. User Responsibilities\nUsers are required to create an account to purchase tickets or access event-related features. You agree to provide accurate and current information and to keep your login credentials secure. You are responsible for all activities conducted under your account.\n\n",null,B.ag,null,null,null,null,null,null)
B.WO=new A.cz("3. Event Organizer Responsibilities\nOrganizers must ensure that all information provided is accurate and up-to-date.\n\n",null,B.ag,null,null,null,null,null,null)
B.WK=new A.cz("4. Ticket Purchases\nTickets purchased via Tixon are intended solely for personal use. You may not resell or transfer tickets unless explicitly allowed by the event organizer. The ticket prices and availability are set by the organizers, and Tixon does not guarantee admission if an event is canceled or rescheduled.\n\n",null,B.ag,null,null,null,null,null,null)
B.WN=new A.cz("5. Prohibited Activities\nYou may not use Tixon for unlawful purposes, including but not limited to, fraud, spamming, hacking, or distributing viruses. Any misuse of the platform can result in account suspension or legal action.\n\n",null,B.ag,null,null,null,null,null,null)
B.WQ=new A.cz("6. Intellectual Property\nAll content on the Tixon platform, including text, images, logos, and software, is the property of Tixon or licensed to Tixon. Unauthorized use of the platform\u2019s content is prohibited.\n\n",null,B.ag,null,null,null,null,null,null)
B.WM=new A.cz("7. Limitation of Liability\nTixon is not liable for any indirect, incidental, or consequential damages, including those resulting from event cancellations, technical issues, or miscommunication by organizers. Your use of the platform is at your own risk.\n\n",null,B.ag,null,null,null,null,null,null)
B.WR=new A.cz("8. Modification of Terms\nTixon reserves the right to change these terms at any time. Continued use of the platform after changes are posted constitutes your acceptance of the modified terms.",null,B.ag,null,null,null,null,null,null)
